ocking your full potential and achieving greatness. Tony’s guidance and support have been instrumental in helping me grow and achieve my goals. If you’re looking for a transformative experience and a coach who genuinely cares about your success, look no further than Coach Tony and 2B Limitless!”", "recommendations/1/name": "Tony Martin", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "CEO | Executive Coach | Innovation Strategist | Builder of Next-Level Performance", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tony-martin-30b5bb3/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACfcvsBQtjKDo80YhU-yyUIBW8fXFHBsgM", "recommendations/2/context": "Brendon was Handy's client", "recommendations/2/date": "December 2, 2022", "recommendations/2/description": "Handy Ong is an absolute champion, he has a great skill knowing how much to push, he seems to always get it right, not to little not to much keeping it fun so your always looking forward to going back for your next class !!!!", "recommendations/2/name": "Handy Ong", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Physiotherapist | Personal Trainer | Swimming Instructor", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/onghandy/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABLbPvUBktzAiIhuQKkAsV1l1SsYF_aUiRY", "recommendations/3/context": "Brendon reported directly to Upward,", "recommendations/3/date": "July 26, 2012", "recommendations/3/description": "I had the pleasure to work for Adrian in 2009\nAdrian is a visionary who always looks at the big picture he shares his vision with the people around him & then guides his team in the desired direction. Adrian is a true professional with amazing knowledge, passion & people skills. Adrian had a great influence on my career that I will always remember.", "recommendations/3/name": "Upward, Adrian", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Director of Culinary at Cathay Pacific - Sodexo Food and facilities Management", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/upward-adrian-7767594/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADSqgoBeKSkMuLHLvlrlGGNJrxjV2-CQT4", "recommendations/4/context": "Brendon was Daniel's client", "recommendations/4/date": "January 30, 2010", "recommendations/4/description": "Daniel supplied supperior products to our Kitchens in Phuket. Daniel strived to have the best products and knowledge of them to support. Daniel shared his commitment and passion with his team giving extensive product training to his associates from study trips visiting the farmers in Australia to seeing the Chefs end product on the plate.\nDaniel took product knowledge to new levels for his team.", "recommendations/4/name": "Daniel Donatelli", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "ENERGY STORAGE Founder Secure Supplies Group Renewable energy to H2 Production / H2 Fueled - MW Class Engine's Healthy", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/danieldonatelli/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALUSNoBsi94wUNHNlcV5z1khVjq-p2R_J0", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Brendon was Tony's client", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "December 29, 2023", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "It is with great enthusiasm that I recommend Brendon, an exceptional professional whose top five Clifton strengths—Includer, Empathy, Achiever, Responsibility, and Developer—demonstrate not only his outstanding work ethic but also his exceptional interpersonal and leadership skills. Brendon's Includer strength is the foundation of his inclusive approach, fostering a collaborative and supportive environment where everyone feels valued and heard.\n\nHis deep well of Empathy enables Brendon to connect with colleagues on a personal level, creating a workplace culture that prioritises understanding and compassion. As an Achiever, Brendon consistently sets high standards for himself and others, driving the team to accomplish goals with a relentless commitment to excellence. His sense of Responsibility is unwavering, ensuring that tasks are not only completed but completed to the highest standards.\n\nBrendon's Developer strength shines through in his ability to recognise and nurture the potential in others, providing mentorship and support to help individuals grow both personally and professionally. His unique combination of strengths makes Brendon an indispensable team member, a compassionate leader, and a catalyst for continuous improvement. I am confident that Brendon's inclusive mindset, empathetic approach, achievement orientation, sense of responsibility, and developmental focus will continue to make a positive impact wherever his professional journey takes him.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Tony Martin", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "CEO | Executive Coach | Innovation Strategist | Builder of Next-Level Performance", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tony-martin-30b5bb3/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACfcvsBQtjKDo80YhU-yyUIBW8fXFHBsgM", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Brendon was senior to 小琼Joan but didn't manage 小琼Joan directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "December 10, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Brendon is extremely focused hardworking Professional Chef. Those who have worked with Brendon know him to be honest reliable and skilled & \nAlways with a Smile.\n Brendon is a world class front man when it comes to making clients feel warm and trusting with his Chef abilities. Food is always made with care and Tastes GREAT!!!\nChef brendon is the best chef to be worked together", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "小琼Joan 王", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "CP Solutions（Asia）Company，Limited - Regional Sales Supervisor", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/小琼joan-王-598140a8/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABbNE0QBYC53Ov6xp1nUIIXkT7oAaFl5Flk", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Jeffrey worked with Brendon on the same team", "recommen