iewed/23/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAknuqYB6Tt_VqXL_oIQRXJG7kQev_c-b44", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/entity_urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAG4eVgB6RQnki6jodcpJ54AdUYpy1_TVbE", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/first_name": "Chaowalit", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/follower_count": "1089", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/headline": "Luxury Hotels and Resorts", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/last_name": "Thinsaku", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/premium": "false", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/public_identifier": "chaowalit-thinsaku-4748019", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAG4eVgB6RQnki6jodcpJ54AdUYpy1_TVbE", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/entity_urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAADtOXIYBrFLbl0-vHgqB7j0kwf2fAPYdaLw", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/first_name": "David", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/follower_count": "286340", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/headline": "Chairman of the Board at Marriott International", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/last_name": "Marriott", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/premium": "true", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/profile_picture": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQE33gwoi3wkqg/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/B56ZT7yD0PGsAc-/0/1739390992033?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=wYHG3ubqEeXCW6013MUJhhas8laggUDPELgZ8aOH-q4", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "davidsmarriott", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAADtOXIYBrFLbl0-vHgqB7j0kwf2fAPYdaLw", "publicIdentifier": "bruno-rotschaedl-hotelier", "recommendations/0/context": "Bruno worked with JoAnne on the same team", "recommendations/0/date": "January 29, 2011", "recommendations/0/description": "During our time together I got to know JoAnne as a truly caring professional who get's the best out of people. She also is a true asset in tough negotiations and challenging business environments; She was well liked among all different levels of the organization and maintained her role as the \"Go-To person\". I truly enjoyed working with her wish her all the best for the future.", "recommendations/0/name": "JoAnne Scidmore", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Director of Human Resources at Hilton Saratoga", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/joanne-scidmore-80983815/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMmHYkBWnp3bbPQt7pFu1Uwj1R3pWWcYTc", "recommendations/1/context": "Bruno managed Andreas directly", "recommendations/1/date": "November 7, 2010", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure working with Andreas during the pre-opening and post-opening. I got to know him as a true professional which was a  driving force. With his leadership, knowledge, passion and dedication to success he put himself and his team as a top contributor to the overall hotel's success. He was able to form a strong new team while communicating at all levels. His eagerness to learn and keep up-to-date is vital and will contribute to any future hotels with upscale culinary operations. I wish Andreas all the best and hope to be able to work with him again.", "recommendations/1/name": "Andreas Hoehne", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Global Director Culinary", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/andreashoehne/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMcRdUB6GcZKVrAgcZr96_g0TUvasc9E5Y", "recommendations/2/context": "Bruno was senior to Robert but didn't manage Robert directly", "recommendations/2/date": "November 5, 2010", "recommendations/2/description": "Robert was instrumental in the opening stage of the CP Kaohsiung. His vast experience and skill set made it easy to establish a high class pastry, bakery, chocolate room and Pastry shop in the hotel. Not only was he a great leader for his team, he also ran a very good production line. With his drive together with his creativity, Robert is perfect match for any upscale Hotel that wants to establish a showcase.", "recommendations/2/name": "Robert Hope", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Pastry Chef Consultant | R&D, Hospitality Sales", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-hope-6aaa5012/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKlcOIBnNER1cTAc6jhQV3CN_3wdxg8WaQ", "recommendations/3/context": "Bruno managed Katarzyna directly", "recommendations/3/date": "September 29, 2010", "recommendations/3/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Kasia at the Warsaw Marriott. She is very professional, a great professional reputation.\nKasia is heavily involved in the operation to ensure her commitments are met. I encountered her as very hardworking and loyal and would love to have the opportunity to work with her again. I only can recommend her as a true asset to any team that is looking for a real professional in the hospitality field and wish her lots of success.", "recommendations/3/name": "Katarzyna Niezgoda", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Regional Director Sales Operations Poland at REVO Hospitality Group/ Hospitality / Sales / MICE / Events", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/katarzynaniezgoda/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAH5_CYBglb9C5gcAnsyhm5dk27JqXBeh0g", "recommendations/4/context": "Bruno was senior to Donald but didn't manage Donald directly", "recommendations/4/date": "September 29, 2010", "recommendations/4/description": "I had the opportunity to work with Mr. Morris in Kaohsiung and can highly recommend him for any Rooms position. He is highly committed to his team, the hotel and always supportive to others. He is hands-on and a go-getter. Being without a Director of Rooms or Resident Manager, Mr. Morris was very capable to plan, train and execute successfully the opening of the hotel by himself. With this he showed a high level of initiative and integrity. I can highly recommend him for any assignment where a strong capable leader is needed.", "recommendations/4/name": "Donald Morris", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Country Manager Korea at Cathay Pacific Airways", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/domorris/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAF68mQB0zxNOY_xCKOsUHFWp7_xvUig1js", "recommendations/5/context": "Bruno managed Pieter directly", "recommendations/5/date": "July 14, 2010", "recommendations/5/description": "During his time in Taiwan, Pieter has shown great initiative and was a driving force in preparing the opening training manuals and giving  presentations to the onboarding team members. Another important part of his assignment was his involvment in conceptualizing the hotel's Italian Restaurant. With his creativity and ownership he developed many creative ideas that made this concept a success. He has a great sense of responsibility and was well liked among all levels of the team.  I wish him all the best in his young career.", "recommendations/5/name": "Pieter Lohuis", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "⚡️Betere zorg door slimmere communicatie!", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pieterlohuis/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMcl6IBecp7eKKaE0ec9j1FJW3a1lpbGdI", "recommendations/6/context": "Bruno was senior to Thijs but didn't manage Thijs directly", "recommendations/6/date": "July 14, 2010", "recommendations/6/description": "Despite his young age, Thijs has shown incredible creativity and leadership skills. He is flexible, challenges himself and continuously  pushes his product to exceed even further. His knowledge, preparation, involvement and leadership skills were crucial for the successful opening of this prime property. I wish him all the best and hope we will have the chance to work together again.", "recommendations/6/name": "Thijs van Rhoon", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Senior Hospitality Leader | Boardmember | Hospitality Asset Management, Operations & Strategic Leadership", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thijs64/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKoI_8BlJ8MgJsNq4vphRXYC77ZhbX4fnI", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Pieter reported directly to Bruno", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "March 4, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/0/descriptio