great leadership attributes.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Gert Noordzy, M.B.A.", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Managing Director | Northside Consulting", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gertnoordzy/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABw5EABdtkfculXHHO_JSpLzpcq9O9fbuc", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Andreas reported directly to Bruno", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "November 7, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I worked with Bruno at the pre-opening and post opening of Crowne Plaza Kaohsiung E-DA World Kaohsiung (Taiwan). He was my EAM /F&B in this hotel and I am very thankful that I had the chance to work with him. For me this was phantastic experience to work with somebody who has so much knowledge and experience in the hospitality Business.\n\nBruno managed to create a F&B team that operated as a family by sharing his experience and his passion with us. \n\nThe time with Bruno made me a different chef/person and he developed me and other people in our team to the next level in our career. \n\nI really hope that we have a chance to work together again in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Andreas Hoehne", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Global Director Culinary", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/andreashoehne/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMcRdUB6GcZKVrAgcZr96_g0TUvasc9E5Y", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Bruno was senior to Thijs but didn't manage Thijs directly", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "November 7, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I had the chance to work with Bruno during the pre- opening of Crowne Plaza Kaohsiung EDA-world and this was a great experience for me. \n\nBruno shared a lot of his experience with me and was always prepared to help out and listen to our opinion, problems, issues or ideas.\n\nBruno is a very friendly leader and gets things done by bringing out the best in his people. Always a smile on his face and even after having a difficult day, Bruno was positive and had the energy to encourage us.  \n\nI hope that our professional paths will cross again in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Thijs van Rhoon", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Senior Hospitality Leader | Boardmember | Hospitality Asset Management, Operations & Strategic Leadership", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thijs64/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKoI_8BlJ8MgJsNq4vphRXYC77ZhbX4fnI", "skills/0/title": "Union Grievances", "skills/1/title": "P&L Management", "skills/2/title": "Event Production", "skills/3/title": "Cultural Diversity", "skills/4/title": "Customer Excellence", "skills/5/title": "Workforce Planning", "skills/6/title": "Crisis Management", "skills/7/title": "Shutdown Planning", "skills/8/title": "Rebranding", "skills/9/title": "Franchise Management", "skills/10/title": "Performance Management", "skills/11/title": "Revenue & Profit Growth", "skills/12/title": "Organizational Leadership", "skills/13/title": "Service Excellence", "skills/14/title": "Business Strategy", "skills/15/title": "Villas", "skills/16/title": "Beaches", "skills/17/title": "Social Media", "skills/18/title": "Leadership Development", "skills/19/title": "Team Building", "totalExperienceYears": "20.6", "totalRecommendationsGiven": "7", "totalRecommendationsReceived": "5", "urn": "ACoAAAHNdNgBvM_wHUrXkfwgiZkGzoTPd3-imao"}$$::jsonb),
