ail orientated, customer focused and passionate hotelier. Juergen, once guided about the bigger picture, has the drive to accomplish projects without delay and showed great leadership skill with the ability to maximise the output of his multi-cultural team.", "recommendations/0/name": "Juergen Purgstaller", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Hotel Manager Viking Cruises Egypt & Owner JP Comsulting", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/purgstaller/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABxwGwBRyM8NxNaFSMfYYSGzC79Yvno1ws", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Christian worked with Denis but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "June 12, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Denis is a splendid person and a high-level professional at work, his ability to adapt and transform problems into opportunities is incredible, great leedership and mentor for his staff who follows him and respects him deeply, what more can we say?  I consider myself lucky to enjoy his esteem and friendship and it is certainly a primary asset for any company that can hire him.\nRegards \nChristian Hammecke ", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Christian Hammecke", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Head of Operations | Training Director | Luxury Dining, Beach Clubs & Lifestyle Concepts | Multi-Unit & Pre-Opening Specialist", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christian-hammecke/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABgs0fQBiwjV5P_XNTaY_ZCSWssAWHpT_jA", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Zul was Denis's client", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "April 23, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Denis is very personable and takes great care of the hotel guests\nAs he did ours. He certainly is a great asset to the company. ", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Zul Somani", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "president at lambeth drugs", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/zul-somani-96756439/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAgXUl8BteJ97ZoZh8tPT9-CePznno6f1wQ", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Juergen reported directly to Denis", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "December 7, 2007", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Mr. Richter helped me to develop my ownership thinking through giving me the trust and space to run the operation independently. He is a great motivator and very creative professional. To increase productivity and GOP without loosing customer satisfaction is also one of his strength.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Juergen Purgstaller", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Hotel Manager Viking Cruises Egypt & Owner JP Comsulting", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/purgstaller/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABxwGwBRyM8NxNaFSMfYYSGzC79Yvno1ws", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Steve worked with Denis but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "August 2, 2007", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Denis really understands the hotel and food and beverage business extremely well.  We worked together in the Philippines.  Denis then went on to Bangkok Thailand to the Amari Watergate Hotel followed by the Movenpick Hotel & Resort in Dubai, UAE  and is now at a luxury tropical paradise called Rex Resorts on the island of St. Lucia in the Caribbean.  He is progressive thinking and yet understands excellent customer service.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Steve Karoul", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "President & CEO, Euro-Asia Consulting, LLC", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/stevekaroul/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAuqeMBWNMDNgeOvRl_9I-3RMTgZWVxpoE", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Dr. Sheila was Denis's client", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "August 1, 2007", "recommendationsReceived/4/descripti